data.description: Wow now this is a piece of paradise on over 11 acres, that sits back off the road and surrounded by woods for all the privacy you will love.  As you drive up the private driveway to the home that opens up with a sloping back yard that already has a chicken and goat pen with a sprawling deck to enjoy the nature to entertaining your family and/or friends that enters from a door wall to a very spacious home with very open and large rooms to a beautiful remodeled kitchen with all the modern technology that overlooks a cozy great room with a warm fireplace for those winters still to come.  There are bathrooms for every bedroom and the master bathroom is one of a kind you will just love along with a basement bathroom that is brand new and beautiful and 2 additional rooms that could be guest rooms or a private office that walks out to a patio for even more space for everyone all this and more to check out with Clarkston schools.
